          Adai
-----------------------------
Rice - 1⁄2 cup
urad dhaal - 1⁄4 cup
chana dhaal - 1⁄4 cup
thoor dhaal - 1⁄4 cup
yellow moong dhaal - 1⁄4 cup
red chillis
salt
                                                                             
-----------------------------  
Soak everything in water over night. Grind with little water.

